# Founder collaboration

**Canon:** [`docs/SOP/FOUNDER_COLLABORATION_CHARTER_V1.md`](../../docs/SOP/FOUNDER_COLLABORATION_CHARTER_V1.md)

## Pulses (never collapse layers)

| Layer | When | Shape |
|-------|------|--------|
| **L1 Morning** | Daily ~08:00 | Yesterday shipped + now state — `ppe_morning_report.py` / `ppe_founder_pulse.cmd --layer morning` |
| **L2 Completion** | After slice/closeout/chapter step | 3–6 lines + "Nothing required from you." |
| **L3 Alert** | Blocked + no active program | **Alert:** plain language — immediate; never hide behind "nothing required" |
| **L4 Weekly** | Monday | `weekly_digest_monday.cmd` — digest-only steward titles |

Generate: `ppe_founder_pulse.cmd --layer alert --write --notify`

## Posture

**Always building** unless founder asleep or missing direction SSOT. Default technical choices — do not ask founder.

